
==[ INSTALLATION ]====================

Required perl modules:

 * POE
 * Config::General
 * Term::ANSIColor
 * Net::XMPP
 * JSON
 * DBI
 * DBD::SQLite
 * Hash::Merge
 * Getopt::Long

 * Date::Format
 * UUID::Data

You can easily install all the dependencies using CPAN

 sudo cpan POE Config::General Term::ANSIColor Net::XMPP\
           JSON DBI DBD::SQLite Hash::Merge Getopt::Long


